 [[File:Rector's palace.jpg|thumb|View of the Rector's Palace.]]
The '''''rector''''' (in Latin; {{lang-it|rettore}}, {{lang-sh|knez}}) was an official in the government of the [[Republic of Ragusa]]. The holder was the head of the executive powers of Ragusa, part of the [[Small Council (Ragusa)|Small Council]] (''Consilium minus''). The rector was seated at the [[Rector's Palace, Dubrovnik|Rector's Palace]].

